    "summary": "Production candidate item catalog for Rummi Poker Grid V4. Effects are original implementations tuned for the current board/hand/discard/market loop, informed by common roguelike deckbuilder patterns.",
    "referencePatterns": [
      "Balatro consumables: held single-use resources with limited slots",
      "Balatro vouchers: persistent economy/shop modifiers",
      "Slay the Spire relics: run-long passive modifiers",
      "Luck be a Landlord items: passive, destroyable, and rarity-weighted utility effects"
    ],
    "policy": [
      "Do not merge items into Jester slots.",
      "Use item subtype and placement to determine battle and market behavior.",
      "Store ids and state counters, not localized text.",
      "Prefer small numeric effects that can ship before full balance pass."
    ]
  },
